Shark XMPP Library
-----------------

License
-------
  This library is licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License.  See
  the COPYING file for more information.


Description
-----------
  Shark is an XMPP Library which borrowed some code from Iris.
  Features implemented:
  - XEP-0004 (Data Forms)
  - XEP-0030 (Feature Discovery)
  - XEP-0050 (Ad-hoc command)
  - XEP-0054 (vcard-temp)
  - XEP-0077 (In-Band Registration)
  - XEP-0114 (Jabber Component Protocol)
  - XEP-0172 (User Nickname)

Build requirements
------------------
libidn-dev
libqt4-dev
